WEBVTT

1
00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:03.350
{\an8}ROSCOSMOS

2
00:08:17.370 --> 00:08:19.120
Good morning. Miss Madison.

3
00:08:19.700 --> 00:08:21.040
Good morning. Pasha.

4
00:08:26.380 --> 00:08:27.936
<i>We are working with the Americans</i>

5
00:08:27.960 --> 00:08:30.606
to resolve the issues
with the transgressing workers.

6
00:08:30.630 --> 00:08:32.896
I would not trust the Americans.

7
00:08:32.920 --> 00:08:35.986
Helios pretends to be
an international company

8
00:08:36.010 --> 00:08:38.656
but it is based in Houston.
right next to NASA.

9
00:08:38.680 --> 00:08:41.850
They serve the interests of Gore
and his lackeys.

10
00:08:46.020 --> 00:08:47.310
What is so funny?

11
00:08:49.230 --> 00:08:54.086
I have met Dev Ayesa and I promise you

12
00:08:54.110 --> 00:09:00.990
he cares more about his own interests
than America's.

13
00:09:01.660 --> 00:09:04.596
Margo is right.
Our intelligence conveys the same.

14
00:09:04.620 --> 00:09:07.856
Now. while the strike is brought
to a close.

15
00:09:07.880 --> 00:09:13.196
all efforts must continue to ensure
the safe capture of this asteroid

16
00:09:13.220 --> 00:09:15.196
and its return to Earth's orbit

17
00:09:15.220 --> 00:09:18.510
under Margo Madison's direction.

18
00:09:19.260 --> 00:09:21.430
Thank you. Director Morozova.

19
00:09:23.230 --> 00:09:29.206
We have updated
2003LC's projected trajectory.

20
00:09:29.230 --> 00:09:35.900
and Tatyana has now calculated
the optimal intercept for <i>Ranger</i>.

21
00:09:36.570 --> 00:09:40.006
She's done some brilliant work.

22
00:09:40.030 --> 00:09:41.870
Very good.

23
00:09:42.830 --> 00:09:44.476
That will be all.

24
00:09:44.500 --> 00:09:46.540
The meeting is adjourned.
Everyone is dismissed.

25
00:09:48.830 --> 00:09:52.130
Margo Madison... stay behind. please.
